Example

This is an example usage of CodeBlock:

python
def code_fn(code_block_input_param: str) -> str:
    return f'Hello {code_block_input_param}'

code_block = CodeBlock(
    reference_name='hello_ccb',
    code=code_fn,
    code_input={'code_block_input_param': 'World'},
)
